delfin_gruppe10.data

Class FileHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • delfin_gruppe10.data.FileHandler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    FileHandlerInterface

    public class FileHandler
extends java.lang.Object
implements FileHandlerInterface
    FileHandler This class handles communication with the .txt files. It is capable of writing to, reading and editing objects stored in .txt files. It can handle both member and competetive swimmer objects.
